high_descs: Turn right, go forward a bit, turn left and go to the counter
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn left, go forward a bit, turn left and go to the fridge
Slice the tomato in the fridge
Turn around, go forward, turn left at the sink
Put the knife in the sink
Turn around, go forward a bit, turn right and go to the fridge
Pick up a tomato slice from the fridge
Move a bit to the right
Put the tomato slice in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the tomato slice from the microwave
Turn around, go forward, turn left at the sink
Put the tomato slice in the sink
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato, cook it and bring it to the sink

high_descs: Take a step right, and then head left to stand in front of the counter space to the right of the stove.
Pick up the butter knife from the counter.
Turn around and carry the knife to the fridge.
Open the fridge and use the knife to slice the tomato.
Turn right and carry the knife to the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn left and head back to the fridge.
Open the fridge and remove a slice of tomato.
Take the tomato to the microwave, which is to your right.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave and then remove once heated.
Turn right and carry the tomato slice to the sink.
Place the tomato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of tomato in the sink.

high_descs: Turn to the right, walk forward a few steps, then turn to the left and walk up to the kitchen counter that is to the right of the oven.
Pick up the knife that is on the counter.
Turn around completely and walk up to the refrigerator.
Slice the tomato that is in the fridge.
Turn around completely, move forward a few steps, then turn to the left and walk up to the kitchen sink.
Place the knife down in the sink.
Turn around completely, move forward a few steps, then turn to the right to go back to the fridge.
Take a slice of tomato out of the fridge.
Move over to the right of the fridge, to the microwave.
Heat the slice of tomato in the microwave before taking it out and closing the door.
Turn around completely, move forward a few steps, then turn to the left to face the kitchen sink.
Place the slice of tomato down in the kitchen sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of tomato in the kitchen sink.
